## 8) Header contract (Layout docs summary)

**Key variables:** `logo`, `store_name`, `categories` (`name`, `url`, `children[]`), `announcement_config` (`text` string[], `type`: simple / slider / marquee), `announcement_text`, `cart_count`, `compare_count`, `wishlist_count`, `is_register_active`, `theme_data`.

**IDs to preserve:**

| ID | Purpose |
|----|---------|
| `header-cart-count` | Cart badge; storefront updates text and `hidden` |
| `header-compare-count` | Compare badge; pair with `compare-click` on parent button |
| `header-wishlist-count` | Inside `<a href="/wishlist">`; no custom event |
| `header-lang-btn`, `header-lang-mobile` | Language controls (hidden if plugin inactive) |
| `header-register`, `header-register-mobile` | Reserved / future; current: `register-btn` + `register-click` |

**Events:** `cart-click` on cart control (often `cart-btn`), `lang-click` on `lang-btn`, `register-click` on `register-btn`, `compare-click` on compare control.

**Doc warnings:** Without `cart-click`, the cart drawer won’t open. Without `id="header-cart-count"`, counts won’t sync. Without `compare-click`, the compare modal won’t open from the header.

---

## 9) Footer contract (summary)

**Variables:** `logo`, `store_name`, `categories` (`name`, `slug`), `pages` (`title`, `slug`), `social` (`type`, `url`, `label`, `icon`), `year`, `payment_img`, `phone`, `email`, `address`, `has_contact`, translated labels (`shop_label`, `help_label`, …), `show_powered`, `theme_data`.

**Newsletter form:** class `footer-subscribe-form`, `novalidate`, HTML5 validation, then `CustomEvent('footer-subscribe', { bubbles: true, detail: { email } })` and `this.reset()`.

