## 10) Product sections — quick variable index

### `breadcrumbs.liquid`

`categories` (`name`, `slug`), `product_name`, `home_text`. Internal links use SPA interception. Placement inside product details may follow admin flag `is_breadcrumbs_in_details`.

### `gallery.liquid`

`images[]`, `mainImage`, `product_name`, `theme_data`. Video: `contains '.mp4'`. Thumbnail / swipe behavior is local Liquid + `script.js` unless the parent re-renders variant data.

### `product-details.liquid`

`product_name`, `price`, `sale_price`, `currency`, `rating`, `reviews_count`, `description` (when `is_description_in_details`), `theme_data`, **`product_id`** for wishlist / compare.

Events: `toggle-wishlist`, `toggle-compare` with `detail: { productId: '{{ product_id }}' }`.

### `product-description.liquid`

`description` (HTML), `description_label`, `policies[]` (`icon`, `title`, `content`), `theme_data`. Optional merge into details per `is_description_in_details`.

### `fixed-buy-button.liquid`

`product_name`, `price`, `sale_price`, `currency`, `thumb`, `buy_now_text`, `quantity`, `disabled`, `hide_quantity`, `increase_disabled`, `theme_data`.

Required events with `bubbles: true`: `buy-now`, `increment-quantity`, `decrement-quantity`.

### `reviews.liquid`

`reviews[]` (`rating`, `user_name`, `comment`, `image`), `reviews_count`, `average_rating`, `average_rating_display`, translated strings, `theme_data`.

Open modal: `data-review-open` on the button, or `review-open` per platform table.

### `related-products.liquid`

Same product contract as homepage listings: `products`, `category`, `section_title`, `currency`, `add`, `shop_now`, `sale`, `theme_data`. Events: `quick-add`, `quick-view`. Shown when the product is not `hide_related_products` and has a category. Horizontal scroll is a good default; storefront typically passes up to ~5 products.

---

## 11) Home sections — summary

### `slider.liquid`

`slides[]`: `image`, `mobile_image` (optional, ≤425px), `url`, `alt`. If `url` is blank, use `<div>` not `<a>`. Use `<picture>` + `<source media>`. First slide `loading="eager"`, rest `lazy`.

### `categories.liquid`

`categories[]`: `name`, `slug`, `thumb`.

### `featured-products.liquid` / `list-products.liquid` / `home-products-grid.liquid`

`products[]`, `category`, `section_title`, `currency`, `add`, `shop_now`, `sale`, `hide_view_all`, `theme_data`.

**Product shape:** `id`, `name`, `slug`, `price`, `sale_price`, `thumb`, `images[]`, `variations[]` (`type`, `props[]` with `name`, `value` for swatches).

**Events:** `quick-add`, `quick-view`, `toggle-wishlist`, `toggle-compare` with `productId`.

### `products-grid.liquid` (search & collections)

Same product contract; `hide_view_all` is always `true` here. The **Load more** button is rendered **outside** Liquid by React; each fetch re-renders this template with the **accumulated** product list.

